public class ListContainerOptions
extends ListOptions
implements Cloneable

Contains options supported in the list container operation.

Usage

The recommended way to instantiate a ListOptions object is to statically import ListContainerOptions.* and invoke a static creation method followed by an instance mutator (if needed):

import static org.jclouds.blobstore.options.ListContainerOptions.Builder.*

BlobStore connection = // get connection Future> list = connection.list("container",inDirectory("home/users").maxResults(1000));

afterMarker

public ListContainerOptions afterMarker(String marker)
Place to continue a listing at. This must be the value returned from the last list object, as not all blobstores use lexigraphic lists.
